The invention relates to the field of internet application development, and discloses a web page popup window method. The method comprises the following steps of: generating an instantiated popup window, and managing the popup window; and loading a popup window page, and generating an instance for calling an external independent page. The invention also discloses a web page popup window device, which comprises a popup window generating module, a popup window management module and a calling module, wherein the popup window generating module is used for generating the instantiated popup window; the popup window management module is used for managing the generated instantiated popup window; and the calling module is used for calling the loaded external independent page and acquiring the popup window instance. According to the method and the device, the external page can be read as popup window contents, mutual parameter transfer and event binding/trigger of the interior of the popup window and a parent window are supported, the popup window and the popup window contents are thoroughly separated, and the maintenance is easy; and by reducing the secondary loading time, the operating experience of a user is effectively promoted, and bandwidth consumption of a server is reduced.

